<TEXT>
Property Trust, of which the Cheng family of Hong Kong holds a stake of more
than 45 per cent, plans to acquire a one third interest in a property joint
venture in Guangzhou, China, in a deal worth Pounds 12m.
The group plans to establish a new holding company in Bermuda which will
take over the existing UK property portfolio as well as purchase the joint
venture stake.
