FT  25 JUL 94 / UK Company News: Gowrings to buy Burger King outlets
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Gowrings, the motor trading and leisure company, has agreed, through its
Gowrings Food Services subsidiary, to buy seven Burger King franchises,
excluding debtors and cash, from Grand Metropolitan for Pounds 3.3m cash.
The company also said it had entered a conditional option agreement with
